Package careerhub.models

Class Staff

java.lang.Object
careerhub.models.User
careerhub.models.Staff
public class Staff extends User
Represents a Career Center Staff user in the Internship Management System. Staff members are responsible for approving or rejecting Company Representative accounts, reviewing internship opportunities, and processing student withdrawal requests. They also have access to all system-wide reporting and filtering tools.

This class stores the staff member’s department and their last-used filter preferences so that menu navigation can restore the user's previous filtering context.
